data.description: Expect to be impressed with this charming 3BR pool home in the well-established Wekiva Park community. You'll be delighted the minute you arrive. This is a corner lot home with lush landscaping (dotted w/palms) surrounding the property. Step inside to open space designed for formal living/dining needs but is versatile to arrange as you see fit. Notice here the highly polished wood flooring - continues throughout the common living space. Walking back, you'll reach the heart of the home - open kitchen and family room that run across the back. Kitchen boasts expansive breakfast bar, granite counters, plenty of cabinet/counter space and a closet pantry. The eat-in area is large enough to seat a crowd. The family room is spacious and provides a great gathering space. There's also direct access to the lanai and pool here. Split bedroom plan with the master suite in the back - ideal for privacy. The bedroom is large enough to add a seating area or private desk, and here you'll enjoy a walk-in closet and classic contemporary bath with dual sink vanity, soaker tub and separate shower. Remaining bedrooms/bath are tucked off the home's hallway, along with the laundry room. The big reason you'll want to own this home is all that you have out back - pristine pool and spa under screen enclosure, covered lanai, and additional open air brick patio. Lanai is a great place for relaxing/dining in the shade, and is set-up for TV viewing. Pool is surrounded by privacy hedging. Entire backyard is fenced and nicely landscaped. Excellent location - less than 1/2 mile to your neighborhood Publix and between 3-5 miles to many major roadways (SR 441, SR 451, SR 429) to whisk you anywhere you need to get to in the greater Orlando area. You'll love living here. Come see all that this special home has to offer.
